_:Nf7001cbdbfd14043b1721c4a7c6f1e9c <http://schema.org/description> "The House of Lords is the second chamber of UK Parliament. It plays a crucial role in examining bills, questioning government action and investigating public policy. Corporate Officers of the House of Lords is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Cabinet Office ." .
